name: Anyfetus
description:
Anyfetus MODEL

A really good and bright model.

You can use the following trigger words if you like:

shiny hair, high contrast, bright, liquid hair

I'll appreciate your support on my Patreon and kofi.

Here is a Form you can request me Lora there (for Free too)

https://forms.gle/h9iuLCCnaEs6W9ZB8
